title: Grateful Dead Live at Madison Square Garden on 1994-10-13
description:
Set 1

Touch Of Gray, Wang Dang Doodle, Loser, Mama Tried*-> Mexicali Blues*, Dupree's Diamond Blues**, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Loose Lucy, Let It Grow

Set 2

Foolish Heart-> Playin' In The Band-> Uncle John's Band-> Drums-> Space-> The Other One-> Wharf Rat-> Johnny B. Goode, E: It's All Over Now Baby Blue

* Weir on acoustic. ** Last played 3/26/90
